---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base.astro";

const meta = {
	description: "I'm a starter theme for Astro.build",
	title: "About",
};
---

<PageLayout meta={meta}>
	<h1 class="title mb-12">About</h1>
	<div class="prose prose-sm prose-cactus max-w-none">
		<p>
    My name is Massimiliano (Max). I have been building software for over fifteen years.
</p>
<p>
    I spent most of my career working on web solutions: CMS platforms, external system integrations, database optimizations. Over the years I have worked with more than a thousand integrations in production: ERPs, CRMs, payment gateways, marketplaces, logistics systems.
</p>
<p>
    I have also worked as a tech lead: code reviews, mentoring, managing small teams. But what I actually enjoy is writing code and solving problems.
</p>
<p>
    When I am not writing code, I work on side projects to explore new practices.
</p>
<p>
    Currently I'm focused on AI and Architecture Methodologies.
</p>
<p>
    If you want to talk about backend, integrations, or just have a chat, reach out.
</p>
	</div>
</PageLayout>
